{"tid":1647188,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指證黑警殺人懸紅計劃","createTime":"2019-10-11T15:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T16:32:48.000Z","uid":296536,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"45ad262c927cd710f186d0fa1d63f82650601ce7","tid":1647188,"uid":296536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:51:46.000Z","msg":"P牌冇得自推，睇完覺得有得諗嘅請幫忙推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n受到港獨之父同大J嘅啟發，其實民間都搞個懸紅計劃有冇得諗？小弟諗左個有別於藍絲懸紅網（每個示威者有個標價）嘅玩法：<br />\n<br />\n搞一個冇上限，或者上限好大（例如十億）嘅眾籌，就好似累積一個Jackpot咁，直至有第一個人提供證據並成功響法庭定黑警謀殺罪，就可以拎走個pool全部錢，亦可以設二獎三獎for其他, 如蓄意傷人罪，濫用職權罪等<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1） Make noise 新玩法<br />\n2）以實際獎勵鼓勵警隊內部篤灰<br />\n3）吸引所有人（包括見錢開眼嘅藍絲）加入監察警隊之列，越多人猴住黑警犯錯佢地就要越收斂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n附加事項：<br />\n以信得過嘅名人/團體名義幫手開，而且確保要有完善保密機制<br />\n<br />\n要知道，成功指證到一單謀殺罪已經會係運動以黎最大核彈，足以粉碎整個黑警集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c3c1efc61a319c462f610cb4d93c3f4c1f65b8","tid":1647188,"uid":296536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39413db6ec04a2fb7b716d6daca4eb3659156273","tid":1647188,"uid":296536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09db1bee35e93e10f3d35a852f14721301b872cc","tid":1647188,"uid":296536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a52b143cef621da3c5cd124a7dc186ad2ad8cbb","tid":1647188,"uid":51068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:54:31.000Z","msg":"墮樓＝生前比人打到骨折　浮屍＝